CHANGES
=======

0.2.0
-----

* release: 0.2.0
* refactor: fix typos and syntax issue
* refactor: bump ubuntu version for github actions to 22.04
* [Improvement] UUID lookup method for VM search
* add: add workflow to build and push container image manually

0.1.0
-----

* release: release of 0.1.0
* fix: prepare for upcoming rename, move guides to wiki
* refactor!: rename commands to vsbmc and vsbmcd
* update: run container as non root
* fix: add permission for diag and refactor some syntax
* add: vSphere role info to README.md
* Update README.md

0.0.8
-----

* release: release of 0.0.8
* fix vm filtering if there is more than 100 virtual machines in vcenter

0.0.7
-----

* release of 0.0.7
* Add GitHub Actions for PyPI
* multiprocess fix - default to 'fork' method
* Update README.md
* Add Baremetal IPI

0.0.6
